{"tid":638643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟睇下你係咪呢種人？","createTime":"2018-04-23T01:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T02:17:10.000Z","uid":147789,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"49d1abab31a8f24e663e2f15edc5b9b177895c76","tid":638643,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T01:39:39.000Z","msg":"如果有件事你做衰咗<br />\n第一時間一定係灰<br />\n然後再望到人地勁過自己<br />\n再灰<br />\n過咗一段時間傷心完<br />\n就覺得自己堅強咗 <br />\n直到下一次再仆直<br />\n純粹覺得自己冇天資就算<br />\n<br />\n其實要做嘅<br />\n係認真諗下自己點解做衰咗<br />\n再諗下點解人地勁過自己<br />\n只要培養到呢種心態<br />\n久而久之一定會有進步<br />\n<br />\n你可能會覺得好老土<br />\n但係老土還老土 有冇用係其次<br />\n祝福各位巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a6cbb2f20d345bd67a8545484031d282b56c4c","tid":638643,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T01:41:06.000Z","msg":"事源今次present練咗好多次<br />\n點知出到去太緊張 比所有人都差<br />\n有感而發<br />\n希望自己都會有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4c8f2c8ffbd25de512052f6e8f8a800826a678","tid":638643,"uid":71154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T02:02:56.000Z","msg":"加油吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個試過中學音樂考試<br />\n我同一個朋友夾琴four hands<br />\n結果佢八分<br />\n我得七分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時嬲到爆<br />\n乜唔係team work 嫁咩<br />\n分一組組又個別俾分<br />\n嗰嗰仲要係我好朋友<br />\n我都好灰機"},{"pid":"de05a738a2c12c09af65abf76fd7c9ab2847d1e8","tid":638643,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T02:17:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分享你地勵志嘅語句"}]}